{"tid":1702352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女懷孕周數同被輪姦日子不符是因為醫生計法","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T07:16:18.000Z","uid":100811,"like":933,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"cf39a27f1d46ef3d574d57b5ceabf08751722676","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"好多準媽媽都唔知點計懷孕週數同預產期 ，今日我地邀請咗婦產科專科醫生馮澍明醫生為大家講解一下:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後一次月經(L.M.P = Last Menstrual Period) 的第一日起為計算懷孕期的首天，不是由受孕的那一天開始計，再以1週7日，4週為一個月計算，滿40週為預產期。未滿37週之生產為早產。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然L.M.P.計算只屬初步估計，因為未必每個準媽媽的週期都穩定為28日，所以醫生會以超聲波來量度生長情況去決定預產期。由於每個胎兒生長情況不一，當醫生在早期超聲波決定了預產期後，預產期便不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n以預產期為界線，預產期時已踏足35歲的話就屬於高齡產婦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">想請問醫護巴絲係唔係咁，有錯請賜正</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輪姦犯死全家 </span></span>"},{"pid":"c7b30d09b84758268517179985535de4246dc8b0","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f6d70eae4263afd03337c65c8fc854e6d9c47c77","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"be5227ecba217a2d6ed2a36bfeec759354659fc3","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"84598fa9fbb62a38049c95c615211be29c92bfb0","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"8fb272e41eeab36b28dfdc647b829ad282a618ed","tid":1702352,"uid":100811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"abc068e6d1e253d4c44b98bdcb1545f83f67caa8","tid":1702352,"uid":137569,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"啱呀你講得"},{"pid":"dfbd32bc67