示出佢係無可能係27/9號或者打後1-2完成受精的話，生物學角度上佢呢個指控係唔成立，咁成件事就變成左從普通角度調查強姦? 咁個有嫌疑嘅dna pool就會變得無限大 (因為嫌疑太多，如果佢唔存在係database就難以查證)"},{"pid":"912535cc7a5b5302abb7be804915a61747fa2f52","tid":1702352,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"a84c995c3acb940eb1c831d04e98a42a7adec2df","tid":1702352,"uid":90422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"冇撚有錯"},{"pid":"0df1d96419527b9f5176f87384325b204bacd0a7","tid":1702352,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8849316016699ff861f2a2d84e638fb03a1cf075","tid":1702352,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af00748175e5a8fd09f7dec72c6135218cd43ef","tid":1702352,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd6a5ebfacf670b891ff07c3d25fd0e6798b5f37","tid":1702352,"uid":63821,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"一般practice入面，排卵（=性交=受精）嗰日係計day14。<br />\n至於點解係day14，純粹係因為一個typical textbook case多數係28day regular cycle，i.e. 最後一次嚟經同排卵會相差14日。<br />\n咁問個patient最後一次嚟經會準過問佢幾時扑過嘢嚟（一方面女仔會mark低經期，另一方面你唔知道連續幾日扑嘢係邊日中，所以問嚟都冇意思）。<br />\nSo LMP defined as Day 0; Fertilization = Day 14<br />\n但又因為每個人經期週期都唔同，啲月經又未必準時，所以會用超聲波再確認。<br />\n<br />\n呢個case嚟講，如果受害人係因姦成孕嘅話，即係話927係2週，今日就係8週"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"752a61c310bdc1f9b6d68430864fe4f02c40dfaa","tid":1702352,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"